            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ASUS 今日在香港公佈推出全新 Zenbook A14 (2025)，這款筆記型電腦主打極致輕量化、強大 AI 整合，及 長效續航力，並搭載 Snapdragon X 系列處理器，適合需要長時間移動工作的專業人士與創作者。Zenbook A14 以 980g 的超輕機身成為目前市場上最輕的 Copilot+ PC，更在硬體設計與 AI 體驗上帶來顯著提升，為使用者提供高效能與便捷性兼備的選擇。</p><p><a title="L1000356" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366699459/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366699459_d8af9b4a00_b.jpg" alt="L1000356" width="906" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295711" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000310-694x491.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="491" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000310-694x491.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000310.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295712" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000316-574x580.jpg" alt="" width="574" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000316-574x580.jpg 574w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000316.jpg 890w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 574px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295716" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000324-694x546.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="546" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000324-694x546.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000324.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295717" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6671-587x580.jpg" alt="" width="587" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6671-587x580.jpg 587w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6671.jpg 911w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 587px" /></p><p><a title="L1000374" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54365623092/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54365623092_cd902d1de8_b.jpg" alt="L1000374" width="1024" height="680" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="L1000382" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366498051/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366498051_9fe26dbc4e_b.jpg" alt="L1000382" width="802" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>全球最輕 980g 機身，Ceraluminum 材質提升耐用度</h2><p>Zenbook A14 以，僅 980g 的重量成為目前全球最輕的 Copilot+ PC，同時配備 14 吋熒幕，超越同尺寸競爭對手，如 MacBook Air（1.24kg, 13.6&#8243;） 及 Galaxy Book4 Edge（1.16kg, 14&#8243;），提供更輕巧便攜的使用體驗。為達到極致輕量化，Zenbook A14 採用 Ceraluminum 陶瓷鋁合金機身材質，這種新技術能讓機身比傳統陽極氧化鋁材輕 30%，但強度提升 3 倍，確保筆電在輕盈的同時依然堅固耐用。此外，Ceraluminum 具備防刮、防指紋、抗污，特性，進一步提升機身的耐久性，讓使用者即使長期攜帶，也能保持機身清潔且美觀。</p><p><a title="L1000403" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366731198/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366731198_f6f024703d_b.jpg" alt="L1000403" width="1024" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="L1000394" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54365626137/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54365626137_a921946396_b.jpg" alt="L1000394" width="723" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295699" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000325-694x441.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="441" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000325-694x441.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000325.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295701" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000336-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000336-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000336.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295718" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6666-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6666-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6666.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2 data-start="956" data-end="991"><strong data-start="960" data-end="989">3K OLED 熒幕與沉浸式音效，視聽體驗全面升級</strong></h2><p data-start="993" data-end="1155">Zenbook A14 配置 14 吋 3K ASUS Lumina OLED 熒幕，提供更細膩的畫面細節與色彩表現，適合專業創作者及高需求視覺體驗的用户。筆電支援 Dolby Atmos 與 Snapdragon Sound 音效認證，讓用户即使在筆電上，也能享受到如家庭劇院般的沉浸式音效體驗。</p><br /><b>
雙 USB-C（Thunderbolt）<br />
HDMI<br />
3.5mm 耳機孔<br />
這樣的設計讓使用者無需額外購買轉接器或 Docking，即可輕鬆連接多種周邊設備，提高使用的便利性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295715" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000322-643x580.jpg" alt="" width="643" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000322-643x580.jpg 643w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000322.jpg 997w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 643px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295714" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000318-560x580.jpg" alt="" width="560" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000318-560x580.jpg 560w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000318.jpg 869w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 560px" /></p><p><a title="L1000381" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366498131/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366498131_b3ce95af60_b.jpg" alt="L1000381" width="786" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2>加大觸控板，支援智慧手勢操作</h2><p>Zenbook A14 配備，加大觸控板，並支援，智慧手勢操作，使用者可以直接透過觸控板來調整，螢幕亮度、音量，甚至，媒體播放控制，讓操作更加直覺，提高生產力。</p><br /><b>
智慧搜尋（可依據關鍵字搜尋圖像與文件）<br />
AI 降噪（提升視訊會議音質）<br />
更完整的 Copilot 2.0 整合<br />
ASUS 內置 Studio Coupe 軟體，提供，統一化影像管理功能，適合內容創作者與專業設計師使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295719" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6673-694x548.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="548" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6673-694x548.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_6673.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295702" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000339-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000339-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000339.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>香港市場獨家版本與售價</h2><p>Zenbook A14 在香港推出兩個版本，售價如下：</p><p>Snapdragon X Elite + 32GB RAM + 1TB SSD：HKD 13,998<br />
Snapdragon X + 32GB RAM + 1TB SSD：HKD 11,998<br />
預購時間：2025 年 3 月 7 日至 3 月 18 日<br />
正式發售：2025 年 3 月 19 日</p><p>預購贈品：</p><p>ASUS AP2600 防刮防水電腦包<br />
MD-102 人體工學滑鼠</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295703" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000345-694x459.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000345-694x459.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/l1000345.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br /><a title="L1000399" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366898130/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366898130_276b706ec7_b.jpg" alt="L1000399" width="977" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="L1000401" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54366730493/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54366730493_e66352a2f7_b.jpg" alt="L1000401" width="1024" height="652" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="L1000364" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54365622537/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54365622537_7ebf763842_b.jpg" alt="L1000364" width="764" height="1024" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="L1000352" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/184475798@N07/54365620647/in/dateposted/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/54365620647_c0e7b99d3c_b.jpg" alt="L1000352" width="1024" height="679" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>【ASUS AI – Zenbook A14 手提電腦規格列表