        </item>
        <item>
            <title>PC  GTA V 免費升級登場，支援 AMD FSR、NVIDIA DLSS</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/gtav-pc-free-update/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gtav-pc-free-update</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/gtav-pc-free-update/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 06:30:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[gta]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[gta 5]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1295642</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>RockStar 宣佈 PC 版《Grand Theft Auto V》今日推出免費升級，玩家可透過 Rockstar Games Launcher、Steam 或 Epic Games 平台體驗。新版本引入先前僅限最新世代主機的功能，並提升現代 PC 的遊戲效能。現有玩家可免費升級並轉移故事模式及線上模式進度，新玩家購買時則同時獲贈強化版與傳承版。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295643" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511118-694x294.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="294" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511118-694x294.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511118.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>今次升級為《GTA Online》帶來多項新功能，包括 Hao’s Special Works 的全新車輛，如 Pegassi Weaponized Ignus、Coil Cyclone II 超級跑車、 Karin S95 跑車、Arbiter GT 美式肌肉車及 Pfister Astron Custom SUV。此外，20 款原有載具亦可於阿浩特製改裝調整性能。為慶祝 GTA+ 登陸 PC，會員可於即日起至 5 月 28 日免費領取 Principe Deveste Eight 超級跑車。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295644" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511133-694x292.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="292" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511133-694x292.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511133.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>玩家更可探索動物生態系統，參與每日野生動物攝影挑戰，並透過更新後的啟動畫面及事業建構器（附 400 萬 GTA 遊戲幣）提升遊戲體驗。全新更新「Oscar Guzman Flies Again」亦同步上線，提供新任務及飛行載具。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295648" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511153-694x293.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="293" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511153-694x293.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511153.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>新版本針對 PC 玩家推出獨有光線追蹤功能，包括環境光遮蔽、全域照明及光線追蹤陰影與反射，並支援 AMD FSR 及 NVIDIA DLSS（未來將加入影格生成）。配合 SSD 及 DirectStorage 技術，載入速度顯著加快，同時支援更高畫質、更高解像度及 Dolby Atmos 音效，語音方面有所提升，支援電影音樂及特效等。玩家更可可體驗自適應扳機的 DualSense 控制器。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295646" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511217-694x293.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="293" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511217-694x293.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511217.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295645" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511225-694x293.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="293" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511225-694x293.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025030511225.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/7551a7k917554a/free-upgrade-for-grand-theft-auto-v-on-pc-now-available">Rockstar Games</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/gtav-pc-free-update/game-channel/">PC  GTA V 免費升級登場，支援 AMD FSR、NVIDIA DLSS</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/gtav-pc-free-update/game-channel/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
