        <item>
            <title>台積電恐變美積電？，台經濟部長：不動搖台灣核心地位</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/tsm-afraid-became-usm/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tsm-afraid-became-usm</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/05/tsm-afraid-became-usm/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 05 Mar 2025 05:36:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[台積電]]>
            </category>
